 Process: <list id="-bb4kjs_32"> <li id="-bb4kjs_33">Select the bank where you will receive the payment.</li> <li id="-bb4kjs_34">Complete the payment process.</li> </list> </step> <step id="-bb4kjs_23"> Finalize the Sale: <list id="-bb4kjs_35"> <li id="-bb4kjs_36">You can choose to print the sales receipt, view it, or simply submit it.</li> </list> </step> </procedure> </chapter>
